	<h1 class="title">随难民迁徙：难民们到了贝尔格莱德，在这里住酒店需要 5 个小时 | 难民危机是怎么回事 七</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Anemona Hartocollis</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-06 09:10:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15693/medium/15693.jpg?1444053379" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


